text: The South West African Labour and Farmers' Party was a political party in Namibia. It was founded on 25 November 1931. ==References== *Klaus Dierks Chronology of Namibian history: from pre-historical times to independent Namibia 1930–1931 Namibia Scientific Society, 1999 pg. 106 Category:Defunct political parties in Namibia Category:Labour parties Category:Political parties established in 1931 Category:1931 establishments in Africa
title: South West African Labour and Farmers' Party
